Metadata: California Sea Grant and the Coastal Ocean Environment: A Summary Report of the California Sea Grant College
University of California Sea Grant College Program
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

In this report of work conducted by the California Sea Grant College, we focus on recent projects that aim to (1) better understand the effects of humans on the coast and coastal ocean environment, (2) try to separate out human effects from natural variations, and (3) diminish or mitigate those effects.
